{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I saw at the back of the barracks-- outside of where the barracks were, past the toilets, I saw a little fire-- around the fire a prisoner with a pot and about 3 or 4 potatoes in it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had to what mention one more thing, which-- because it's the title of my next book.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have to mention it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "At the-- at first, there were the sayings, 'If it only doesn't get worse,' you've heard-- you remember that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The next thing was-- you heard-- it was the last thing, the phrase, 'Oh, to survive, be it only with a dry, plain potato.' It was-- that was in Yiddish, so that translation would be 'dry.' But the meaning would be 'a plain potato,' in other words, the minimum of sustenance to survive.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "People pledged not to want any more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that is why I made it-- the plain potato-- I made it the title of my second book, that I adhered to that pledge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] thing was that I saw this man having cooked his potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was crawling on all fours, leaving my blanket behind because I didn't want to have it get dirty on the dry spot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would-- nobody would come to steal it anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody moved anymore, practically, very few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And wading through the stuff, practically, and getting near to him like a wildcat-- and as he was taking the first potato to his mouth, I was grabbing it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not being able to run, I shoved away on all fours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was angry, but didn't want to go after me because he would have, have to leave his potatoes behind.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took the potatoes out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
